      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Showdown in the Arena",
        "Client": "Rowdy Showman",
        "Description": "Gather \u0027round, gather \u0027round! Today\r\nwe have a show packed with fur and\r\nfury! Anjanath! Mizutsune! Zinogre!\r\nSparks will fly! Fire will burn! Bubbles\u2014\r\nd-does that say bubbles? It does. Uh...\r\nOK. Bubbles will, um, bubble! Who dares\r\nchallenge this trifecta of trepidation!",
        "Target": "Hunt all target monsters",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Le combat du si\u00E8cle",
        "Client": "Homme de spectacle",
        "Description": "Approchez, approchez ! Un spectacle\r\nau poil vous attend aujourd\u0027hui !\r\nUn Anjanath, un Mizutsune et un\r\nZinogre ! Tremblez face aux \u00E9clairs\r\nfoudroyants, aux flammes br\u00FBlantes\r\net aux bulles... euh... rondes ? Qui\r\nosera affronter ce trio infernal ?",
        "Target": "Chasser tous les monstres",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Scontro nell\u0027Arena",
        "Client": "Showman chiassoso",
        "Description": "Attenzione! Attenzione! Lo\r\nspettacolo di oggi prevede\r\nfuria e pellicce! Un Anjanath,\r\nun Mizutsune e uno Zinogre! Ne\r\nvedremo delle bolle? Bolle?\r\nC\u0027\u00E8 scritto bolle? Ehm... OK!\r\nChi sfider\u00E0 il temibile trio?",
        "Target": "Caccia tutti i mostri assegnati",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Kr\u00E4ftemessen in der Arena",
        "Client": "R\u00FCpelhafter Schausteller",
        "Description": "Menschen, Tiere, Sensationen! Heute\r\nhaben wir ein Spektakel aus Zorn und\r\nZotteln! Anjanath! Mizutsune! Zinogre!\r\nFunken fliegen! Feuer brennt! Blasen--\r\nS-Steht da Blasen? Tatsache. \u00C4h... Okay.\r\nBlasen, \u00E4hm, blubbern! Wer wagt sich an\r\ndieses Dreiergespann der Beklemmung?",
        "Target": "Erjage alle Zielmonster.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Duelo en la Arena",
        "Client": "Artista alborotador",
        "Description": "\u00A1Damas, caballeros y ni\u00F1os!\r\nEl Anjanath, el Mizutsune y\r\nel Zinogre, \u00A1el tr\u00EDo maldito!\r\nFieros, astutos y mortales.\r\n\u00BFQui\u00E9n se las ver\u00E1 con ellos?\r\nCazadores, \u00A1el espect\u00E1culo\r\ndebe continuar!",
        "Target": "Caza todos los objetivos",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0421\u0440\u0430\u0436\u0435\u043D\u0438\u0435 \u043D\u0430 \u0430\u0440\u0435\u043D\u0435",
        "Client": "\u0428\u0443\u043C\u043D\u044B\u0439 \u0448\u043E\u0443\u043C\u0435\u043D",
        "Description": "\u041F\u043E\u0434\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442\u0435, \u043F\u043E\u0434\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442\u0435, \u0423 \u043D\u0430\u0441\r\n\u0441\u0435\u0433\u043E\u0434\u043D\u044F \u043C\u0435\u0445 \u0438 \u044F\u0440\u043E\u0441\u0442\u044C! \u0410\u043D\u044C\u044F\u043D\u0430\u0442!\r\n\u041C\u0438\u0434\u0437\u0443\u0446\u0443\u043D\u044D! \u0417\u0438\u043D\u043E\u0433\u0440! \u0418\u0441\u043A\u0440\u044B!\r\n\u041E\u0433\u043E\u043D\u044C! \u041F\u0443\u0437\u044B\u0440\u0438! \u0421\u0442\u043E\u043F, \u0442\u0430\u043A\r\n\u0438 \u043D\u0430\u043F\u0438\u0441\u0430\u043D\u043E \u2014 \u0022\u043F\u0443\u0437\u044B\u0440\u0438\u0022? \u0425\u043C. \u0414\u0430.\r\n\u041B\u0430\u0434\u043D\u043E. \u041F\u0443\u0437\u044B\u0440\u0438! \u0422\u0440\u0435\u043F\u0435\u0449\u0438\u0442\u0435 \u0436\u0435\r\n\u043F\u0435\u0440\u0435\u0434 \u044D\u0442\u043E\u0439 \u0443\u0436\u0430\u0441\u043D\u043E\u0439 \u0442\u0440\u043E\u0438\u0446\u0435\u0439!",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u0432\u0441\u0435\u0445 \u043E\u0442\u043C\u0435\u0447\u0435\u043D\u043D\u044B\u0445 \u043C\u043E\u043D\u0441\u0442\u0440\u043E\u0432",
        "Fail": "\u0421\u0447\u0435\u0442\u0447\u0438\u043A \u043D\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0434\u044B \u0434\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442 \u0434\u043E 0\r\n\u0438\u043B\u0438 \u0438\u0441\u0442\u0435\u043A\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F"
      },
      {
        "Language": "POL",
        "Name": "Widowisko na Arenie",
        "Client": "Ha\u0142a\u015Bliwy showman",
        "Description": "Chod\u017Acie, chod\u017Acie! Dzisiaj widowisko\r\npe\u0142ne futra i furii! Anjanath!\r\nMizutsune! Zinogr! Polec\u0105 iskry! B\u0119d\u0105\r\nbucha\u0107 p\u0142omienie! B\u0105ble... Zaraz, tu\r\njest napisane \u201Eb\u0105ble\u201D? Ano jest.\r\nOk... B\u0105ble b\u0119d\u0105... b\u0105belkowa\u0107! Kto\r\nstawi czo\u0142o potr\u00F3jnej dawce grozy?",
        "Target": "Upoluj wszystkie cele",
        "Fail": "Nagroda = 0 lub koniec czasu"
